with that nonsense.

00:07:15.749 --> 00:07:17.284 position:30% line:89% align:start
But it's true.

00:07:17.317 --> 00:07:19.219 position:7% line:83% align:start
They do roam around in there,
don't they?

00:07:19.253 --> 00:07:20.687 position:30% line:89% align:start
