00:16:27.567 --> 00:16:28.969 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:16:31.671 --> 00:16:33.740 position:16% line:89% align:start
(wind whistling softly)

00:16:57.831 --> 00:17:00.600 position:7% line:83% align:start
-(screams) Don't let us fall!
-(grunts, shouts)

00:17:00.633 --> 00:17:03.737 position:21% line:83% align:start
-What? Fall where?
-Just don't let go!

00:17:03.770 --> 00:17:05.172 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:17:08.742 --> 00:17:09.976 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:17:10.011 --> 00:17:11.611 position:35% line:89% align:start
(panting)

00:17:36.669 --> 00:17:39.140 position:16% line:89% align:start
(footsteps clank softly)

00:17:42.642 --> 00:17:44.145 position:38% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:17:45.079 --> 00:17:46.546 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:04.731 --> 00:18:07.334 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's like Lagos's picture.

00:18:09.702 --> 00:18:12.073 position:16% line:89% align:start
(wind whooshing softly)

00:18:12.106 --> 00:18:14.075 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:18:14.108 --> 00:18:17.677 position:5% line:89% align:start
Lagos, you've got to be kidding.

00:18:17.710 --> 00:18:20.214 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you an Invert?

00:18:20.247 --> 00:18:22.682 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're upside down.

00:18:22.715 --> 00:18:24.351 position:7% line:89% align:start
What do you mean upside down?

00:18:24.385 --> 00:18:27.687 position:24% line:83% align:start
Look, I don't know
what's going on around here,

00:18:27.720 --> 00:18:29.223 position:21% line:89% align:start
but look around you.

00:18:29.256 --> 00:18:31.392 position:10% line:83% align:start
Can't you see for yourself?!
You're on the ceiling!

00:18:31.425 --> 00:18:33.094 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sorry, hate to tell you,

00:18:33.127 --> 00:18:34.928 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I'm pretty sure
you're the one on the ceiling.

00:18:34.961 --> 00:18:37.831 position:7% line:83% align:start
Yeah, right. Well, I'm pretty
sure I know up from dow...

00:18:37.864 --> 00:18:38.999 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:18:39.033 --> 00:18:41.768 position:27% line:89% align:start
The bat person.

00:18:41.801 --> 00:18:43.070 position:35% line:89% align:start
I knew it.

00:18:43.104 --> 00:18:45.039 position:5% line:83% align:start
-You're one of them, aren't you?
-Huh?

00:18:45.072 --> 00:18:47.007 position:19% line:83% align:start
You hang upside down.
I should've known.

00:18:47.041 --> 00:18:48.109 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, calm down.

00:18:48.142 --> 00:18:49.343 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why is this happening to me?

00:18:49.376 --> 00:18:51.045 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stop. Geez.

00:18:51.078 --> 00:18:52.379 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let me go, okay?!

00:18:52.413 --> 00:18:54.248 position:35% line:89% align:start
Just wait!

00:18:54.281 --> 00:18:56.883 position:13% line:83% align:start
Do you mind telling me what
it is exactly I've done to you?

00:18:56.916 --> 00:18:59.120 position:7% line:89% align:start
Uh, it's 'cause you-- I mean...

00:18:59.153 --> 00:19:01.188 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nothing, that's what.

00:19:02.789 --> 00:19:06.826 position:10% line:89% align:start
And I won't, Invert or not.

00:19:17.171 --> 00:19:19.373 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sorry about that.

00:19:19.406 --> 00:19:21.408 position:7% line:89% align:start
You saved my life, didn't you?

00:19:22.775 --> 00:19:25.379 position:30% line:83% align:start
What happened?
Was someone after you?

00:19:25.412 --> 00:19:27.814 position:24% line:89% align:start
Now what do I do?

00:19:31.784 --> 00:19:33.820 position:16% line:89% align:start
(wind whooshing softly)

00:19:39.193 --> 00:19:40.693 position:33% line:89% align:start
Listen, I...

00:19:40.727 --> 00:19:42.129 position:10% line:89% align:start
(siren blaring in distance)

00:19:42.163 --> 00:19:44.064 position:33% line:83% align:start
-What's that?
-Sorry, I-I've got to get back.

00:19:44.098 --> 00:19:45.199 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:45.232 --> 00:19:46.400 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
To school.

00:19:46.433 --> 00:19:47.434 position:38% line:83% align:start
PATEMA:
No!

00:19:47.468 --> 00:19:50.204 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait. Please, don't go!

00:19:50.237 --> 00:19:52.039 position:13% line:89% align:start
You can't leave me alone.

00:19:52.072 --> 00:19:54.141 position:13% line:89% align:start
But I've got civics class.

00:19:54.175 --> 00:19:56.310 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't be absent.
They watch us.

00:19:56.343 --> 00:19:59.746 position:16% line:83% align:start
What's more important, me
or some stupid class at school?!

00:19:59.779 --> 00:20:00.947 position:35% line:89% align:start
(whimpers)

00:20:02.216 --> 00:20:05.685 position:16% line:83% align:start
You don't have to worry.
I'll come back after.

00:20:06.487 --> 00:20:08.455 position:33% line:89% align:start
You promise?

00:20:08.489 --> 00:20:10.224 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:20:10.257 --> 00:20:12.359 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:20:36.950 --> 00:20:38.419 position:16% line:83% align:start
-(music stops abruptly)
-Don't forget, okay?

00:20:38.452 --> 00:20:39.819 position:38% line:89% align:start
I won't.

00:20:40.853 --> 00:20:41.955 position:7% line:89% align:start
(music starts, stops abruptly)

00:20:41.989 --> 00:20:43.856 position:7% line:89% align:start
And don't tell the bat people.

00:20:43.890 --> 00:20:45.858 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Okay.
-(music starts, stops abruptly)

00:20:45.892 --> 00:20:47.361 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, and I'm hungry, too.

00:20:47.394 --> 00:20:49.530 position:13% line:83% align:start
Something tells me you're
a real princess, aren't you?

00:20:49.563 --> 00:20:51.232 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Yes, I am.
-(music resumes)

00:20:51.265 --> 00:20:53.866 position:21% line:83% align:start
And it would be best
if you would remember that.

00:20:55.002 --> 00:20:57.438 position:27% line:83% align:start
My name's Age.
What should I call you?

00:20:57.471 --> 00:20:59.306 position:38% line:89% align:start
Patema.

00:21:01.475 --> 00:21:03.810 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:21:10.551 --> 00:21:13.753 position:27% line:89% align:start
Amazing. I flew!

