 <i>Remember...</i>

00:23:01.228 --> 00:23:05.265 position:35% line:71% align:start
 <i>IZAMURA:</i>
 <i>When our planet was afflicted</i>
 <i>by The Great Change,</i>

00:23:05.299 --> 00:23:07.501 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>many lives were lost</i>
 <i>when people were</i>

00:23:07.534 --> 00:23:10.104 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>carried off into the sky.</i>

00:23:10.137 --> 00:23:13.107 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>You see, we citizens of Aiga,</i>

00:23:13.140 --> 00:23:15.509 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>who remain</i>
 <i>firmly rooted to the earth,</i>

00:23:15.542 --> 00:23:17.977 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>are left to preserve humanity.</i>

00:23:18.011 --> 00:23:19.646 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>As a result,</i>

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:23.283 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Aiga's the only true world</i>
 <i>in which humanity exists.</i>

00:23:24.284 --> 00:23:27.087 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>There is no world but Aiga.</i>

00:23:27.121 --> 00:23:30.624 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>We must keep our eyes</i>
 <i>firmly on our feet,</i>

00:23:30.657 --> 00:23:33.460 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>follow the laws</i>
 <i>and maintain order,</i>

00:23:33.494 --> 00:23:37.464 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>as we continue to preserve</i>
 <i>our precious land.</i>

00:23:37.498 --> 00:23:40.701 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>That barren wasteland</i>
 <i>that lies beyond the cliff,</i>

00:23:40.734 --> 00:23:45.305 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>that malevolent light</i>
 <i>that comes from the sky,</i>

00:23:45.339 --> 00:23:47.107 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>-they are to be...</i>
-(beep, video stops)

00:23:47.141 --> 00:23:49.009 position:38% line:83% align:start
TEACHER:
Three demerit points, Age.

00:23:49.042 --> 00:23:50.344 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you know why?

00:23:50.377 --> 00:23:52.212 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
I was listening.

00:23:52.246 --> 00:23:55.682 position:35% line:71% align:start
TEACHER:
Yes, but unfortunately
you were also looking off

00:23:55.716 --> 00:23:58.452 position:10% line:83% align:start
in an unpleasant direction,
weren't you?

00:23:59.987 --> 00:24:03.290 position:35% line:83% align:start
As usual,
your brain is inverted.

00:24:03.323 --> 00:24:05.092 position:19% line:83% align:start
-AGE (quietly): What?
-(chuckles)

00:24:06.393 --> 00:24:10.531 position:38% line:71% align:start
TEACHER:
Can anyone tell me
why life here in Aiga is ideal?

00:24:10.564 --> 00:24:12.132 position:38% line:89% align:start
Anyone?

00:24:14.201 --> 00:24:15.669 position:41% line:89% align:start
Well?

00:24:15.702 --> 00:24:18.372 position:27% line:83% align:start
For Age's sake,
we can discuss this

00:24:18.405 --> 00:24:20.641 position:7% line:89% align:start
for the entire assembly period.

00:24:20.674 --> 00:24:22.276 position:35% line:89% align:start
(gasping)

00:24:22.309 --> 00:24:23.710 position:44% line:71% align:start
BOY:
We follow the laws,
maintain order

00:24:23.744 --> 00:24:25.646 position:5% line:89% align:start
and keep our eyes on the ground.

00:24:25.679 --> 00:24:27.414 position:38% line:83% align:start
TEACHER:
Correct.

00:24:27.448 --> 00:24:29.450 position:16% line:89% align:start
Law and order are vital.

00:24:30.484 --> 00:24:32.186 position:27% line:83% align:start
I have been told
that you were not

00:24:32.219 --> 00:24:34.354 position:27% line:83% align:start
in the dormitory
last night, Age.

00:24:34.388 --> 00:24:37.324 position:27% line:83% align:start
One who does not
stay in line here will--

00:24:37.357 --> 00:24:39.326 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you listening to me?!

00:24:39.359 --> 00:24:41.128 position:21% line:83% align:start
You will not qualify
to be a citizen

00:24:41.161 --> 00:24:43.263 position:7% line:89% align:start
just by showing up for class.

00:24:43.297 --> 00:24:46.767 position:38% line:83% align:start
(scoffs)
Like father like son, I suppose.

00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:48.368 position:41% line:89% align:start
(beep)

00:24:49.803 --> 00:24:52.072 position:24% line:89% align:start
(camera whirring)

00:24:54.107 --> 00:24:55.309 position:27% line:89% align:start
(clears throat)

00:24:55.342 --> 00:24:56.643 position:27% line:89% align:start
But don't worry.

00:24:56.677 --> 00:24:59.346 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm not giving up on you
just yet.

00:24:59.379 --> 00:25:02.449 position:7% line:83% align:start
You, too, will have to shoulder
the burden of our future.

00:25:02.483 --> 00:25:04.251 position:30% line:83% align:start
And that means
your presence here

00:25:04.284 --> 00:25:06.487 position:16% line:89% align:start
carries some importance.

00:25:06.520 --> 00:25:09.022 position:10% line:83% align:start
What happened to your father
was a shame,

00:25:09.056 --> 00:25:12.493 position:13% line:83% align:start
but I believe we must not
dwell on the past.

00:25:12.526 --> 00:25:14.061 position:35% line:89% align:start
But, sir?

00:25:14.094 --> 00:25:15.529 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yes?
-If I'm not mistaken,

00:25:15.562 --> 00:25:18.565 position:21% line:83% align:start
the laws say nothing
about looking up at the sky.

00:25:18.599 --> 00:25:22.503 position:7% line:83% align:start
(sighs) I can't believe we need
to look at page six again.

00:25:22.536 --> 00:25:25.105 position:27% line:89% align:start
(tablet beeping)

00:25:25.138 --> 00:25:28.141 position:13% line:83% align:start
Nothing good can come from
looking into the sky

00:25:28.175 --> 00:25:31.311 position:10% line:83% align:start
and the souls of the sinners
who've been carried into it.

00:25:31.345 --> 00:25:35.115 position:19% line:83% align:start
But is it really a sin
to fall into the sky?

00:25:35.148 --> 00:25:37.284 position:24% line:89% align:start
So it is written.

00:25:37.317 --> 00:25:39.720 position:16% line:89% align:start
It is a despicable sin.

00:25:42.856 --> 00:25:45.392 position:30% line:83% align:start
-(straining)
-You can't go to the surface!

00:25:45.425 --> 00:25:47.127 position:30% line:89% align:start
Talk to Elder.

00:25:47.160 --> 00:25:50.030 position:19% line:71% align:start
-I can't just sit here
and do nothing!
-(shouts)

00:26:03.877 --> 00:26:06.179 position:10% line:89% align:start
(footsteps running on grass)

00:26:07.714 --> 00:26:09.483 position:16% line:83% align:start
-(footsteps approaching)
-(gasps)

00:26:10.784 --> 00:26:13.053 position:27% line:89% align:start
(door creaking)

00:26:16.890 --> 00:26:18.725 position:33% line:89% align:start
Uh, Patema?

00:26:18.759 --> 00:26:20.193 position:30% line:83% align:start
-You're late!
-(gasps)

00:26:20.227 --> 00:26:21.395 position:35% line:83% align:start
Do you know
how boring it is here?

00:26:21.428 --> 00:26:23.864 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry.
They kept me after class.

00:26:23.897 --> 00:26:25.532 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Here.
-(grunts)

00:26:29.369 --> 00:26:30.537 position:38% line:89% align:start
(sniffs)

00:26:30.571 --> 00:26:31.805 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yum!

00:26:32.873 --> 00:26:34.207 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:26:46.853 --> 00:26:49.723 position:7% line:89% align:start
(groans) I feel kind of weird.

00:26:49.756 --> 00:26:53.594 position:7% line:83% align:start
(gasps) Maybe eating your food
made me lighter.

00:26:53.627 --> 00:26:54.828 position:27% line:89% align:start
(grunts softly)

00:26:59.700 --> 00:27:01.234 position:30% line:89% align:start
(gasps softly)

00:27:10.377 --> 00:27:11.578 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Patema.
-Huh?

00:27:11.612 --> 00:27:13.280 position:16% line:89% align:start
Does the sky scare you?

00:27:13.313 --> 00:27:14.781 position:38% line:89% align:start
The sky?

00:27:14.815 --> 00:27:16.917 position:35% line:83% align:start
You mean
where you're looking now?

00:27:16.950 --> 00:27:18.652 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's right.

00:27:18.685 --> 00:27:20.387 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, the sky.

00:27:20.420 --> 00:27:22.522 position:16% line:89% align:start
Of course it scares me.

00:27:22.556 --> 00:27:24.358 position:19% line:89% align:start
Doesn't it scare you?

00:27:24.391 --> 00:27:27.661 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well, tonight you can see the
stars, so I guess I like it.

00:27:27.694 --> 00:27:29.563 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Stars?
-(chuckles)

00:27:29.596 --> 00:27:31.331 position:27% line:83% align:start
You don't know
about stars either?

00:27:31.365 --> 00:27:33.266 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't know anything
about this world,

00:27:33.300 --> 00:27:35.535 position:27% line:89% align:start
so why would I?

00:27:35.569 --> 00:27:37.771 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, come look
at the stars, okay?

00:27:37.804 --> 00:27:38.772 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:27:38.805 --> 00:27:41.241 position:38% line:83% align:start
-No way!
-Just try.

00:27:41.274 --> 00:27:43.176 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm scared to look down!
Forget it!

00:27:43.210 --> 00:27:45.278 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Really?
-Yeah. Of course!

00:27:47.347 --> 00:27:48.548 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
All right.

00:27:53.687 --> 00:27:55.455 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:27:56.423 --> 00:27:58.458 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:28:18.712 --> 00:28:20.747 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:28:36.496 --> 00:28:37.931 position:33% line:83% align:start
(whispers):
Beautiful.

00:28:39.866 --> 00:28:43.804 position:21% line:5% align:start
You're the first one
who's ever said that.

00:28:43.837 --> 00:28:47.474 position:21% line:5% align:start
But they really are.

00:28:47.507 --> 00:28:50.343 position:19% line:5% align:start
More so than anything
I've seen where I come from.

00:28:51.945 --> 00:28:54.347 position:13% line:89% align:start
My dad told me about them.

00:28:54.381 --> 00:28:55.582 position:35% line:89% align:start
Your dad?

00:28:55.615 --> 00:28:57.718 position:27% line:83% align:start
He really liked
looking at the sky.

00:28:58.652 --> 00:29:01.388 position:27% line:83% align:start
He always said
he wanted to fly off into it.

00:29:02.456 --> 00:29:05.425 position:21% line:83% align:start
He even made himself
a machine to do that.

00:29:06.460 --> 00:29:08.328 position:41% line:83% align:start
PATEMA:
To fly? How?

00:29:08.361 --> 00:29:10.564 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm not sure.

00:29:10.597 --> 00:29:12.466 position:24% line:89% align:start
I don't remember.

00:29:12.499 --> 00:29:14.202 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why don't you ask him?

00:29:16.770 --> 00:29:20.607 position:44% line:71% align:start
AGE:
For some reason,
everyone was against him flying.

00:29:20.640 --> 00:29:22.876 position:27% line:83% align:start
They all thought
it was bad luck.

00:29:22.909 --> 00:29:24.911 position:10% line:89% align:start
Of course I knew it wasn't.

00:29:24.945 --> 00:29:27.814 position:13% line:83% align:start
I skipped school that day
so I could go watch.

00:29:28.782 --> 00:29:30.817 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:29:51.538 --> 00:29:53.573 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:30:02.649 --> 00:30:05.819 position:7% line:89% align:start
They all said God punished him.

00:30:13.560 --> 00:30:15.062 position:38% line:5% align:start
But why?

00:30:15.096 --> 00:30:17.999 position:10% line:5% align:start
It was a great thing he did,
wasn't it?

00:30:22.769 --> 00:30:26.406 position:41% line:71% align:start
