I'm glad I came to this world.

00:30:56.937 --> 00:30:59.006 position:27% line:89% align:start
(wind whistling)

00:31:03.077 --> 00:31:05.345 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:31:17.024 --> 00:31:19.026 position:27% line:89% align:start
(keys clacking)

00:31:19.060 --> 00:31:22.063 position:38% line:83% align:start
IZAMURA:
Mm. Definitely inverted.

00:31:22.096 --> 00:31:24.131 position:13% line:89% align:start
Did it fall into the sky?

00:31:24.165 --> 00:31:25.932 position:30% line:89% align:start
Or perhaps...

00:31:25.966 --> 00:31:28.568 position:44% line:71% align:start
JAKU:
Sir, this incident
