00:31:28.602 --> 00:31:31.138 position:33% line:83% align:start
at some point
below the barren zone,

00:31:31.172 --> 00:31:33.140 position:13% line:89% align:start
near the Education Center.

00:31:33.174 --> 00:31:35.042 position:10% line:89% align:start
Increase surveillance there.

00:31:35.076 --> 00:31:37.044 position:16% line:89% align:start
Note even minor changes.

00:31:37.078 --> 00:31:38.645 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, sir.

00:31:38.678 --> 00:31:40.480 position:7% line:89% align:start
This may provide us with a clue

00:31:40.513 --> 00:31:42.749 position:35% line:83% align:start
as to where
the rest of them might be.

00:31:42.782 --> 00:31:45.518 position:19% line:89% align:start
And once we find them,

00:31:45.552 --> 00:31:49.756 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm sure that
