00:31:49.789 --> 00:31:51.791 position:27% line:89% align:start
(keys clacking)

00:32:02.736 --> 00:32:04.804 position:16% line:89% align:start
(wind whooshing softly)

00:32:06.806 --> 00:32:09.643 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
