to go explore,

00:32:16.150 --> 00:32:18.052 position:21% line:89% align:start
to find a new world.

00:32:18.085 --> 00:32:19.786 position:13% line:89% align:start
There were books about it,

00:32:19.819 --> 00:32:23.190 position:35% line:83% align:start
and Lagos--
he once gave me a picture.

00:32:23.224 --> 00:32:25.226 position:10% line:89% align:start
The most beautiful picture.

00:32:25.259 --> 00:32:26.826 position:27% line:89% align:start
I still have it.

00:32:27.827 --> 00:32:29.196 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
Lagos?

00:32:29.230 --> 00:32:30.998 position:41% line:83% align:start
PATEMA:
Someone important.

00:32:33.600 --> 00:32:35.635 position:41% line:83% align:start
AGE:
So, I guess

00:32:35.669 --> 00:32:38.239 position:21% line:83% align:start
you don't like where
you're from either, huh?

00:32:38.272 --> 00:32:40.573 position:41% line:83% align:start
PATEMA:
No, that's not true.

00:32:40.607 --> 00:32:42.943 position:7% line:89% align:start
