00:33:51.711 --> 00:33:53.880 position:38% line:89% align:start
But how?

00:33:53.913 --> 00:33:55.149 position:35% line:89% align:start
Grab hold.

00:33:55.182 --> 00:33:57.251 position:27% line:89% align:start
(wind whooshing)

