00:34:04.824 --> 00:34:06.327 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's okay. Don't worry.

00:34:06.360 --> 00:34:08.962 position:19% line:83% align:start
They say only sinners
fall into the sky.

00:34:10.064 --> 00:34:11.865 position:19% line:83% align:start
