00:34:11.898 --> 00:34:13.267 position:24% line:89% align:start
Of course I don't.

00:34:23.177 --> 00:34:24.644 position:30% line:89% align:start
I can do this.

00:34:24.677 --> 00:34:26.013 position:24% line:89% align:start
I trust you, Age.

00:34:26.047 --> 00:34:28.815 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's the spirit.
