00:34:36.090 --> 00:34:38.125 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:34:42.829 --> 00:34:45.066 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:34:45.099 --> 00:34:47.234 position:27% line:83% align:start
