00:35:05.252 --> 00:35:07.221 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:35:07.254 --> 00:35:09.223 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait! Slow down!

00:35:09.256 --> 00:35:11.992 position:19% line:83% align:start
I get it. Your weight
makes me a lot lighter.

00:35:12.026 --> 00:35:15.062 position:13% line:83% align:start
Girls don't like it when
you talk like that, you know!

00:35:19.133 --> 00:35:20.234 position:44% line:89% align:start
Age.

00:35:20.267 --> 00:35:23.070 position:7% line:89% align:start
Age! Watch where you're going!

00:35:26.673 --> 00:35:29.809 position:27% line:89% align:start
(both screaming)

