(both grunt)

00:35:35.349 --> 00:35:37.617 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Patema whimpering)

00:35:38.319 --> 00:35:40.054 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:35:45.292 --> 00:35:47.228 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Age panting)

00:35:54.801 --> 00:35:57.438 position:7% line:83% align:start
-I think you can make it back.
