00:36:02.775 --> 00:36:04.178 position:21% line:89% align:start
You mean we can fly?

00:36:04.211 --> 00:36:05.745 position:19% line:89% align:start
Are you sure? (gasps)

00:36:05.778 --> 00:36:08.882 position:33% line:83% align:start
To get there,
we need to go behind them.

00:36:08.915 --> 00:36:10.284 position:41% line:83% align:start
PATEMA:
Behind them?

00:36:10.317 --> 00:36:12.386 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:36:14.321 --> 00:36:16.056 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait!

00:36:16.090 --> 00:36:17.358 position:27% line:89% align:start
We can make it.

00:36:23.230 --> 00:36:24.398 position:30% line:89% align:start
(both scream)

00:36:24.431 --> 00:36:26.100 position:33% line:89% align:start
(Age grunts)

00:36:26.133 --> 00:36:28.169 position:27% line:89% align:start
(wind whistling)

00:36:30.904 --> 00:36:33.107 position:27% line:89% align:start
It worked! Wow.

00:36:33.140 --> 00:36:34.375 position:30% line:89% align:start
We're flying!

00:36:44.951 --> 00:36:45.986 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:36:52.493 --> 00:36:54.761 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:36:59.500 --> 00:37:01.734 position:30% line:89% align:start
