00:37:49.083 --> 00:37:50.251 position:30% line:89% align:start
They took her.

00:37:50.284 --> 00:37:52.419 position:27% line:83% align:start
-(gasps softly)
-What was that?

00:37:53.520 --> 00:37:56.123 position:24% line:89% align:start
They took Patema.

00:37:56.156 --> 00:37:58.292 position:7% line:89% align:start
I just-- I wanted to help her.

00:37:58.325 --> 00:38:01.028 position:38% line:83% align:start
TEACHER:
He's not making any sense.

00:38:01.061 --> 00:38:02.563 position:24% line:89% align:start
They attacked us!

00:38:02.596 --> 00:38:05.299 position:21% line:83% align:start
Th-They're the ones
not making sense!

00:38:05.332 --> 00:38:07.401 position:27% line:89% align:start
Behave yourself.

00:38:11.572 --> 00:38:13.873 position:16% line:89% align:start
(footsteps approaching)

00:38:17.144 --> 00:38:18.878 position:27% line:89% align:start
Please leave us.

00:38:35.129 --> 00:38:36.297 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:38:36.330 --> 00:38:38.132 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:38:43.037 --> 00:38:44.971 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:38:51.412 --> 00:38:54.981 position:10% line:83% align:start
What you met near the fence
was not human.

00:38:55.015 --> 00:38:59.286 position:13% line:83% align:start
If your desire is to live,
you will forget her.

00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:02.855 position:33% line:83% align:start
Just leave
all the hard questions to us.

00:39:02.889 --> 00:39:06.460 position:24% line:83% align:start
