she looks like a girl.

00:39:08.562 --> 00:39:10.531 position:33% line:83% align:start
-(grunting)
-(laughs)

00:39:13.367 --> 00:39:15.469 position:16% line:89% align:start
I won't tell you again.

00:39:15.502 --> 00:39:20.174 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'd hate for you to have an
accident like your father did.

00:39:20.207 --> 00:39:22.242 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:39:44.365 --> 00:39:46.433 position:21% line:89% align:start
(footsteps receding)

00:39:52.072 --> 00:39:54.108 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:40:29.042 --> 00:40:30.444 position:30% line:83% align:start
-(door opens)
-(gasps)

00:40:30.477 --> 00:40:32.446 position:33% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:40:35.716 --> 00:40:37.284 position:24% line:89% align:start
What do you want?

00:40:39.052 --> 00:40:40.421 position:24% line:89% align:start
Send me back home.

00:40:40.454 --> 00:40:42.922 position:7% line:89% align:start
I hate this upside-down world.

00:40:45.459 --> 00:40:47.261 position:24% line:89% align:start
Upside-down, huh?

00:40:47.294 --> 00:40:49.463 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm afraid you're mistaken.

00:40:49.496 --> 00:40:52.599 position:13% line:83% align:start
After all, you're the one
hanging from the ceiling.

00:40:52.633 --> 00:40:55.235 position:10% line:89% align:start
Don't you think that's odd?

00:40:55.269 --> 00:40:57.438 position:13% line:83% align:start
It seems quite clear to me
that perhaps

00:40:57.471 --> 00:41:01.475 position:21% line:83% align:start
you don't understand
why you were born an Invert.

00:41:04.278 --> 00:41:05.646 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Patema gasps)

00:41:05.679 --> 00:41:07.414 position:35% line:71% align:start
IZAMURA:
