to harness energy from gravity.

00:41:14.655 --> 00:41:16.723 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>(explosive rumbling)</i>

00:41:16.757 --> 00:41:19.726 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>But Mother Nature would not</i>
