00:41:25.566 --> 00:41:28.235 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>These people</i>
 <i>and everything they created</i>

00:41:28.268 --> 00:41:31.004 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>all fell up into the sky.</i>

00:41:32.673 --> 00:41:36.976 position:19% line:83% align:start
All except, of course,
for our ancestors.

00:41:37.778 --> 00:41:40.214 position:7% line:89% align:start
We established the land of Aiga

00:41:40.247 --> 00:41:44.084 position:5% line:83% align:start
to ensure that nothing like this
would ever happen again.

00:41:44.117 --> 00:41:46.620 position:13% line:83% align:start
And to bring eternal peace
to our society

00:41:46.653 --> 00:41:49.122 position:16% line:89% align:start
based on law and order.

00:41:52.125 --> 00:41:56.129 position:19% line:83% align:start
However, some for whom
gravity was reversed

00:41:56.163 --> 00:41:58.232 position:21% line:89% align:start
managed not to fall.

00:41:58.265 --> 00:42:00.367 position:5% line:89% align:start
That filth abandoned the surface

00:42:00.400 --> 00:42:03.403 position:16% line:83% align:start
and burrowed themselves
underground.

00:42:03.437 --> 00:42:07.274 position:24% line:83% align:start
We have made Aiga
into a perfect society.

00:42:07.307 --> 00:42:09.276 position:21% line:83% align:start
So what do you think
would happen if we allowed

00:42:09.309 --> 00:42:12.045 position:30% line:83% align:start
Inverted blood
to contaminate ours?

00:42:12.079 --> 00:42:15.782 position:19% line:83% align:start
We cannot expose Aiga
to such impurities,

00:42:15.816 --> 00:42:18.385 position:16% line:83% align:start
especially from sinners
like yourself,

00:42:18.418 --> 00:42:22.356 position:7% line:83% align:start
who will then be swallowed up
by the sky!

00:42:22.389 --> 00:42:24.825 position:27% line:89% align:start
Sinners? How so?

00:42:24.858 --> 00:42:28.428 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hmm. Allow me to introduce you.

00:42:28.462 --> 00:42:31.798 position:10% line:83% align:start
After all, this unfortunate
situation all began

00:42:31.832 --> 00:42:34.735 position:7% line:83% align:start
-when an Invert showed up here.
-(gasps)

