♪

00:42:47.748 --> 00:42:49.783 position:33% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:42:54.855 --> 00:42:57.157 position:24% line:89% align:start
(liquid burbling)

00:43:00.327 --> 00:43:02.329 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:43:16.510 --> 00:43:18.712 position:16% line:83% align:start
