before you

00:43:18.745 --> 00:43:20.847 position:30% line:83% align:start
was taken in
by one of our citizens,

00:43:20.881 --> 00:43:24.585 position:7% line:83% align:start
and encouraged him to threaten
Aiga's law and order.

00:43:24.618 --> 00:43:26.286 position:24% line:89% align:start
See? All inverted.

00:43:26.320 --> 00:43:28.288 position:10% line:89% align:start
And that got me to thinking:

00:43:28.322 --> 00:43:31.191 position:5% line:83% align:start
perhaps there were other Inverts
hidden away somewhere,

00:43:31.224 --> 00:43:34.795 position:7% line:83% align:start
who might also try to come here
and threaten Aiga's sanctity.

00:43:36.697 --> 00:43:39.766 position:13% line:83% align:start
That man refused to talk,
right to the very end.

00:43:39.800 --> 00:43:41.368 position:35% line:83% align:start
-(shouts)
-But still,

00:43:41.401 --> 00:43:43.870 position:10% line:89% align:start
his ordeal won him nothing!

00:43:45.238 --> 00:43:47.107 position:35% line:89% align:start
(shouting)

00:43:47.841 --> 00:43:49.443 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:43:49.476 --> 00:43:50.877 position:27% line:89% align:start
(wind whistling)

00:43:52.245 --> 00:43:53.413 position:35% line:89% align:start
(screams)

00:43:53.447 --> 00:43:55.282 position:35% line:89% align:start
(whimpers)

00:43:56.850 --> 00:43:59.353 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're very heavy.

00:43:59.386 --> 00:44:02.889 position:16% line:83% align:start
I could easily drop you.
(laughs)

00:44:07.894 --> 00:44:09.896 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, that's right.

