(grunts) Man, this is scary.

00:46:04.878 --> 00:46:06.780 position:30% line:89% align:start
Almost there.

00:46:06.813 --> 00:46:09.382 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:46:09.416 --> 00:46:10.784 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:46:10.817 --> 00:46:12.486 position:35% line:89% align:start
(gasping)

00:46:18.425 --> 00:46:20.694 position:10% line:89% align:start
(stammers) Wait, come back!

00:46:22.896 --> 00:46:25.499 position:16% line:89% align:start
You know Patema, right?

00:46:27.834 --> 00:46:30.437 position:16% line:83% align:start
Wait, what?! Do you know
where I can find her?!

00:46:31.872 --> 00:46:34.608 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Tell me! Where is she?!
-(grunting)

00:46:35.675 --> 00:46:37.677 position:13% line:89% align:start
(both shouting, grunting)

00:46:40.680 --> 00:46:41.882 position:35% line:89% align:start
(panting)

00:46:41.915 --> 00:46:43.717 position:27% line:89% align:start
That was close.

00:46:43.750 --> 00:46:45.519 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ow. Stupid fence.

00:46:45.552 --> 00:46:48.388 position:16% line:83% align:start
I could hold Patema down
with my weight.

00:46:48.421 --> 00:46:49.923 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, yeah. Where is she?

00:46:50.857 --> 00:46:52.759 position:21% line:89% align:start
You know, don't you?

00:46:52.793 --> 00:46:54.561 position:19% line:89% align:start
Come on, just tell me.

00:47:02.103 --> 00:47:04.504 position:21% line:89% align:start
Did they catch her?

00:47:06.840 --> 00:47:08.775 position:19% line:89% align:start
They did, didn't they?

00:47:08.809 --> 00:47:10.644 position:7% line:89% align:start
Just tell me the truth, please!

00:47:10.677 --> 00:47:12.679 position:27% line:83% align:start
-I was with her.
-(gasps)

00:47:12.712 --> 00:47:14.314 position:21% line:83% align:start
You just stood there
and watched?!

00:47:16.883 --> 00:47:18.385 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:47:18.418 --> 00:47:19.886 position:16% line:89% align:start
What could I have done?

00:47:22.389 --> 00:47:23.723 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Porta grunts)

00:47:30.831 --> 00:47:33.733 position:44% line:83% align:start
Hey,
if your gravity's reversed...

00:47:34.734 --> 00:47:37.537 position:38% line:83% align:start
Patema--
she's in that tower, right?

00:47:39.073 --> 00:47:40.440 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Okay, you!
-(gasps)

00:47:40.473 --> 00:47:42.043 position:16% line:83% align:start
-You're coming with me.
-Huh?

00:47:42.076 --> 00:47:43.643 position:35% line:83% align:start
-(stammers)
-Just come on!

00:47:43.677 --> 00:47:44.945 position:35% line:89% align:start
(stammers)

00:47:44.978 --> 00:47:47.014 position:27% line:89% align:start
(rope creaking)

00:47:50.450 --> 00:47:52.819 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey, he's coming.

00:47:52.853 --> 00:47:54.688 position:27% line:89% align:start
That was quick.

00:47:54.721 --> 00:47:55.990 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:47:56.023 --> 00:47:58.092 position:30% line:83% align:start
-One and-- Oh!
-What?

00:47:58.125 --> 00:48:00.861 position:24% line:83% align:start
-It's really light.
-Do you think he fell?

00:48:00.894 --> 00:48:02.729 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey, come on, that's enough.

00:48:02.762 --> 00:48:03.897 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Bite your...
-Huh?

00:48:03.930 --> 00:48:05.532 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tongue!
-(screams)

00:48:05.565 --> 00:48:08.102 position:35% line:83% align:start
-(gasping)
-What the hell?

00:48:08.135 --> 00:48:09.402 position:35% line:89% align:start
An Aigan!

00:48:09.436 --> 00:48:11.438 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hey, Porta, what are you doing?

00:48:11.471 --> 00:48:13.473 position:7% line:89% align:start
Quiet down! We'll talk later.

00:48:13.506 --> 00:48:15.575 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now take us to see Elder!

00:48:16.643 --> 00:48:18.678 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:48:29.190 --> 00:48:30.957 position:35% line:89% align:start
(panting)

00:48:30.992 --> 00:48:32.826 position:10% line:83% align:start
-It's one of the bat people!
-Whoa!

00:48:32.859 --> 00:48:34.028 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait! (sighs)

00:48:34.061 --> 00:48:36.030 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:48:36.063 --> 00:48:38.132 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:48:43.570 --> 00:48:45.639 position:27% line:89% align:start
(quiet chatter)

00:48:51.811 --> 00:48:53.613 position:41% line:83% align:start
ELDER:
Keep them all out of here.

00:48:53.647 --> 00:48:55.548 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Understood?
-Got it.

00:49:03.090 --> 00:49:04.491 position:38% line:89% align:start
(groans)

00:49:04.524 --> 00:49:06.660 position:13% line:89% align:start
What have you done, Porta?

00:49:06.693 --> 00:49:09.763 position:21% line:83% align:start
Really? Is that all
any of you can say to me?

00:49:15.535 --> 00:49:17.737 position:13% line:89% align:start
Everything is upside down.

00:49:17.771 --> 00:49:19.806 position:24% line:83% align:start
I certainly hope
none of the children saw him.

00:49:19.839 --> 00:49:20.907 position:35% line:89% align:start
Children?

00:49:20.941 --> 00:49:22.609 position:38% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:49:22.642 --> 00:49:25.179 position:27% line:83% align:start
We do not teach
our children here about Aiga.

00:49:25.212 --> 00:49:27.081 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's one of our rules.

00:49:27.114 --> 00:49:29.083 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's important
that they grow up right.

00:49:29.116 --> 00:49:30.917 position:5% line:89% align:start
Here we go with the rules again.

00:49:30.951 --> 00:49:33.220 position:16% line:83% align:start
The rules exist to stop
this very thing from happening!

00:49:33.254 --> 00:49:34.688 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Why can't you see...
-Forget the rules!

00:49:34.721 --> 00:49:36.690 position:21% line:83% align:start
-They've got Patema!
-Huh?

00:49:36.723 --> 00:49:38.491 position:38% line:89% align:start
(growls)

00:49:38.525 --> 00:49:40.860 position:30% line:83% align:start
I was worried
that might be the case.

00:49:40.894 --> 00:49:42.529 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
It's true, right?

00:49:42.562 --> 00:49:43.930 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where is she?

00:49:43.964 --> 00:49:45.865 position:24% line:83% align:start
Somewhere inside
the Control Center.

00:49:45.899 --> 00:49:47.534 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's a tower in Aiga.

00:49:47.567 --> 00:49:49.103 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's located
right above the danger zone.

00:49:49.136 --> 00:49:50.904 position:41% line:83% align:start
ELDER:
You went there?!

00:49:50.937 --> 00:49:53.074 position:41% line:71% align:start
 <i>PORTA:</i>
 <i>I drifted back down here</i>
 <i>with him.</i>

00:49:53.107 --> 00:49:55.508 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>You see,</i>
 <i>their weight cancels ours.</i>

00:49:55.542 --> 00:49:57.078 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Which means, with his help,</i>

00:49:57.111 --> 00:49:58.778 position:16% line:83% align:start
we can get in the tower
from there.

00:49:58.812 --> 00:50:00.647 position:41% line:71% align:start
ELDER:
We will not
break the rules twice!

00:50:00.680 --> 00:50:02.716 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
Ah, you and your stupid rules!

00:50:02.749 --> 00:50:05.552 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sick of hearing it,
you old goat!

00:50:05.585 --> 00:50:07.288 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Forget the rules!
-You be quiet!

00:50:07.321 --> 00:50:09.290 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
Who made those rules, anyway?!

00:50:09.323 --> 00:50:10.757 position:41% line:83% align:start
ELDER:
Shut your mouth!

00:50:10.790 --> 00:50:13.127 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
(grunts) You make me, old man!

00:50:13.160 --> 00:50:15.929 position:27% line:89% align:start
(both grunting)

00:50:15.962 --> 00:50:17.897 position:41% line:83% align:start
ELDER:
Is that a photograph?

00:50:17.931 --> 00:50:20.201 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh, yeah.

00:50:22.936 --> 00:50:25.139 position:13% line:89% align:start
Looks like it's from Aiga.

00:50:25.172 --> 00:50:27.874 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't know how many times
I told that fool Lagos

00:50:27.907 --> 00:50:29.609 position:7% line:89% align:start
not to show her those things.

00:50:29.642 --> 00:50:30.910 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who's this guy Lagos?

00:50:30.944 --> 00:50:32.579 position:13% line:83% align:start
Was he Patema's boyfriend
or something?

00:50:32.612 --> 00:50:33.813 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:50:33.847 --> 00:50:35.882 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's just some loon
who went to Aiga.

00:50:35.915 --> 00:50:39.987 position:7% line:83% align:start
He should have known not to go
to such a horrible place.

00:50:40.021 --> 00:50:41.888 position:21% line:89% align:start
What horrible place?

00:50:41.921 --> 00:50:43.991 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:50:45.159 --> 00:50:46.726 position:10% line:89% align:start
It can be difficult to grasp

00:50:46.760 --> 00:50:49.030 position:30% line:83% align:start
how terrifying
a place like that can be

00:50:49.063 --> 00:50:51.332 position:33% line:83% align:start
until you see
you have nowhere to stand.

00:50:51.365 --> 00:50:55.635 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's a very different world
she's seeing now-- poor girl.

00:50:55.668 --> 00:50:57.837 position:19% line:83% align:start
She must be terrified
in a place like that.

00:50:57.871 --> 00:51:00.241 position:30% line:83% align:start
No, she's not.
She's doing just fine.

00:51:00.274 --> 00:51:03.244 position:30% line:83% align:start
-She said so.
-Of course she told you that.

00:51:03.277 --> 00:51:05.545 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's just the way she is.

00:51:06.946 --> 00:51:10.184 position:13% line:83% align:start
I remember she acted the
same way when the Chief died,

00:51:10.217 --> 00:51:13.653 position:7% line:83% align:start
even though his death left her
without any remaining family.

00:51:13.686 --> 00:51:16.790 position:21% line:83% align:start
I remember. She just
hid in her room and cried.

00:51:16.823 --> 00:51:18.925 position:10% line:89% align:start
She didn't want us to know.

00:51:18.958 --> 00:51:20.660 position:16% line:89% align:start
So she appeared strong?

00:51:20.693 --> 00:51:23.830 position:19% line:83% align:start
No offense, but you're
too upside down to understand.

00:51:23.863 --> 00:51:25.932 position:30% line:83% align:start
How could you
possibly understand

00:51:25.965 --> 00:51:27.700 position:19% line:89% align:start
anything about Patema?

00:51:30.171 --> 00:51:32.839 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that may be so.

00:51:32.872 --> 00:51:36.709 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's possible
I don't understand at all.

00:51:37.811 --> 00:51:39.313 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:51:39.346 --> 00:51:41.048 position:33% line:89% align:start
I was happy.

00:51:42.083 --> 00:51:44.818 position:35% line:83% align:start
She said
the stars were beautiful,

00:51:44.851 --> 00:51:47.654 position:27% line:83% align:start
and she listened
about my father.

00:51:47.687 --> 00:51:50.824 position:21% line:83% align:start
I never told anyone
about that before.

00:51:50.857 --> 00:51:55.695 position:13% line:83% align:start
But when she was captured,
I couldn't do anything to help.

00:51:56.763 --> 00:51:59.632 position:19% line:83% align:start
I didn't even think of
trying to rescue her.

00:52:00.733 --> 00:52:02.702 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:52:02.735 --> 00:52:03.937 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll do anything.

00:52:03.970 --> 00:52:06.340 position:21% line:89% align:start
You have to help me.

00:52:13.114 --> 00:52:14.747 position:27% line:89% align:start
(grunts softly)

00:52:16.117 --> 00:52:17.717 position:38% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:52:19.752 --> 00:52:21.788 position:27% line:5% align:start
(quiet rustling)

00:52:35.768 --> 00:52:37.837 position:33% line:89% align:start
(whooshing)

00:52:42.409 --> 00:52:45.179 position:41% line:71% align:start
ELDER:
We call this area here
the danger zone,

00:52:45.212 --> 00:52:50.151 position:7% line:83% align:start
because this is where the tower
reaches down to the ground.

00:52:50.184 --> 00:52:52.752 position:27% line:83% align:start
Once, long ago,
it was used for communication

00:52:52.785 --> 00:52:54.421 position:21% line:89% align:start
between us and Aiga.

00:52:54.455 --> 00:52:56.323 position:24% line:89% align:start
Or so I've heard.

00:53:01.395 --> 00:53:02.795 position:35% line:89% align:start
So this...

00:53:03.998 --> 00:53:06.733 position:38% line:83% align:start
...is the
Control Center basement?

00:53:10.504 --> 00:53:12.373 position:41% line:83% align:start
ELDER:
It's all but abandoned now.

00:53:12.406 --> 00:53:15.309 position:27% line:83% align:start
There's no way
of getting through.

00:53:20.481 --> 00:53:22.882 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
It comes down this deep?

00:53:22.916 --> 00:53:25.852 position:41% line:71% align:start
ELDER:
I'm not sure
why it was abandoned,

00:53:25.885 --> 00:53:28.189 position:16% line:89% align:start
but the Chief once said

00:53:28.222 --> 00:53:31.225 position:10% line:83% align:start
that Aiga hoped to flourish
by cutting ties with us

00:53:31.258 --> 00:53:32.926 position:16% line:89% align:start
and forgetting its past.

00:53:32.959 --> 00:53:35.196 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's worry about
the history lesson later.

00:53:35.229 --> 00:53:37.797 position:38% line:83% align:start
Right now
let's just sneak in there.

00:53:37.830 --> 00:53:40.234 position:27% line:89% align:start
(rope creaking)

00:53:40.267 --> 00:53:42.336 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:53:42.369 --> 00:53:45.939 position:13% line:83% align:start
We simply cannot let Aiga
take anyone else.

00:53:45.972 --> 00:53:47.474 position:21% line:89% align:start
If they catch you...

00:53:47.508 --> 00:53:50.344 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm going to save her.
I'll go alone if I have to.

00:53:50.377 --> 00:53:52.346 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh, yeah?!
Well, I was about to say that!

00:53:52.379 --> 00:53:53.880 position:7% line:89% align:start
You'll both have to cooperate

00:53:53.913 --> 00:53:55.382 position:10% line:83% align:start
for this to have any chance
of working.

00:53:55.416 --> 00:53:57.251 position:30% line:83% align:start
PORTA and AGE:
We are well aware of that!

00:53:57.284 --> 00:54:00.487 position:41% line:71% align:start
ELDER:
Remember, even though
you're upside down...

00:54:00.521 --> 00:54:02.223 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're the one
standing on the ceiling.

00:54:02.256 --> 00:54:04.857 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
Come on, let's go. Stay alert.

00:54:04.891 --> 00:54:06.926 position:27% line:89% align:start
You stay alert.

00:54:06.960 --> 00:54:08.928 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:54:21.175 --> 00:54:23.043 position:38% line:71% align:start
IZAMURA:
It would seem
that I have accomplished

00:54:23.077 --> 00:54:26.746 position:30% line:83% align:start
far more than
the leader who came before.

00:54:27.880 --> 00:54:30.117 position:30% line:83% align:start
And that girl
finding her way here

00:54:30.150 --> 00:54:32.987 position:7% line:83% align:start
means there are a lot more rats
hiding in the sewer.

00:54:33.020 --> 00:54:34.854 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you think?

00:54:34.887 --> 00:54:36.257 position:7% line:89% align:start
We could just interrogate her.

00:54:36.290 --> 00:54:38.058 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, there's no need to rush.

00:54:39.059 --> 00:54:40.860 position:10% line:89% align:start
She'll soon come to realize

00:54:40.893 --> 00:54:43.998 position:13% line:83% align:start
that I hold absolute power
over her.

00:54:44.031 --> 00:54:48.901 position:10% line:83% align:start
Once she's been softened up,
she'll tell us anything we ask.

00:54:50.837 --> 00:54:54.008 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Understood?
-Uh, it's not that, sir.

00:54:54.041 --> 00:54:58.845 position:38% line:71% align:start
IZAMURA:
(chuckles) The look on her face
as she clung to me...

00:54:58.878 --> 00:55:02.216 position:30% line:83% align:start
I look forward
to seeing that again.

00:55:02.249 --> 00:55:03.950 position:35% line:89% align:start
(chuckles)

00:55:06.320 --> 00:55:08.289 position:27% line:83% align:start
The Invert girl
has been transferred.

00:55:08.322 --> 00:55:11.158 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thank you. Good work.

00:55:11.191 --> 00:55:14.428 position:13% line:83% align:start
But why is she in the hall
of the top floor?

00:55:14.461 --> 00:55:17.398 position:41% line:71% align:start
JAKU:
Apparently,
that frightens Inverts.

00:55:28.941 --> 00:55:30.977 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:55:48.961 --> 00:55:50.431 position:30% line:83% align:start
-(heads bump)
-(both groan)

00:55:51.365 --> 00:55:52.832 position:33% line:89% align:start
(both growl)

00:55:55.135 --> 00:55:57.204 position:5% line:89% align:start
(Porta and Age grunting quietly)

00:56:00.107 --> 00:56:02.476 position:24% line:89% align:start
(camera whirring)

00:56:02.509 --> 00:56:04.111 position:24% line:89% align:start
(static crackles)

00:56:09.982 --> 00:56:11.518 position:27% line:89% align:start
(both grunting)

00:56:37.411 --> 00:56:39.480 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:57:08.542 --> 00:57:09.610 position:41% line:83% align:start
PORTA:
Damn.

00:57:09.643 --> 00:57:12.012 position:10% line:89% align:start
I can't go over there, Age.

00:57:12.045 --> 00:57:14.081 position:5% line:89% align:start
You go. I'll find another route.

00:57:14.114 --> 00:57:15.282 position:41% line:89% align:start
Porta?

00:57:16.216 --> 00:57:18.452 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:57:19.753 --> 00:57:22.055 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll be right behind you, okay?

00:57:32.032 --> 00:57:34.101 position:16% line:89% align:start
(wind whistling softly)

00:57:58.592 --> 00:58:00.461 position:35% line:89% align:start
Beautiful.

00:58:01.462 --> 00:58:04.064 position:33% line:89% align:start
(whimpering)

00:58:04.097 --> 00:58:07.167 position:27% line:89% align:start
Help... help me.

00:58:08.502 --> 00:58:10.137 position:44% line:89% align:start
Age.

00:58:11.238 --> 00:58:13.207 position:30% line:83% align:start
-(quiet clink)
-(gasps)

00:58:19.413 --> 00:58:20.647 position:30% line:89% align:start
(quiet click)

00:58:27.287 --> 00:58:28.655 position:44% line:83% align:start
AGE:
I'm sorry.

00:58:28.689 --> 00:58:30.724 position:24% line:89% align:start
I left you alone.

00:58:33.193 --> 00:58:35.262 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:58:38.165 --> 00:58:39.500 position:27% line:89% align:start
(crying softly)

00:58:46.106 --> 00:58:48.175 position:24% line:89% align:start
(crying continues)

00:58:58.285 --> 00:59:00.354 position:30% line:89% align:start
Lagos is dead.

00:59:02.289 --> 00:59:03.590 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:59:09.363 --> 00:59:11.398 position:44% line:89% align:start
♪

00:59:18.372 --> 00:59:21.241 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, I met your family
back home.

